{"tid":194708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【準備好打仗】俄羅斯伊朗警告特朗普 再炸敍利亞會「軍事報復」","createTime":"2017-04-10T07:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T08:57:57.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a14ea0c8de58441e38960982e3b742a686f87148","tid":194708,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170410/large/1491793225_9090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170410%2Flarge%2F1491793225_9090.jpg&h=b13db2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國上周向敍利亞空軍基地發射多枚巡航導彈，俄羅斯及伊朗軍方聯手警告美國總統特朗普，揚言一旦美國再向敍利亞發動更多空襲，兩國將會採取軍事行動報復。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯、伊朗軍方與伊斯蘭武裝組織真主黨（Hezbollah）發表聯合聲明，指特朗普突然炮轟敍利亞巴沙爾政權是越界之舉，「由現在起我們會以武力回應任何超越紅線的行動，而美國知道我們有能力好好回應」。<br />\n英國外相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）提議在七大工業國（G7）峯會上向俄羅斯施壓，迫使莫斯科不再支持巴沙爾政權，否則俄羅斯會面臨新制裁。俄羅斯駐倫敦使館在社交網暗示，如果俄羅斯在敍利亞問題上被下達「最後通牒」，將可能發生「真正的戰爭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170410/56544499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170410%2F56544499&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=1bb97770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170410%2F56544499&h=e129b3f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170410/56544499</a>"},{"pid":"ca8092450696a3bc189af4f940832db6f55ccc56","tid":194708,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"開戰，但戰場會係敘利亞"},{"pid":"61b8a3b31c82f0ad2f69e983b8b52039658b3d5e","tid":194708,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ari-sensei.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fari-sensei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F043.jpg&h=c92bb629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be8c6b0331cd2e3f1a3bb1c027fa51329fdec042","tid":194708,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"日俄戰爭<br />\n<br />\n飛彈 打哂去敘利亞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}